item.title: How can I make a CUSTOM teleport?
item.dc:creator: @Superd00d Superd00d
item.description:
@Superd00d wrote:

[quote=“Thickertech, post:3, topic:323659”]try this

if(command.equalsIgnoreCase("gohere")&& playerRights >= 0){ teleportToX = absX; teleportToY = absY; sendMessage("You have teleported somewhere"); }[/quote] use that one.

item.title: How can I make a CUSTOM teleport?
item.dc:creator: @LilXCj LilXCj
item.description:
@LilXCj wrote:

Find

public void teleportTo

and add

if(command.equals("gohere")) {
teleportTo(void ints go here);
sendMessage("You have been teleported!");
}

To where-ever your commands are handled.
